{"tid":2330491,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梓樂死因　個官今日又唔老實","createTime":"2020-12-18T05:16:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-18T07:24:10.000Z","uid":261647,"like":11,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"e53ecbd5986f49357b3a4b6e42690921506cb899","tid":2330491,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T05:16:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2917750001794405\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flynnleiwong%2Fposts%2F2917750001794405&d=PGKZrCzpIeFm7bz4D1EKrSlkmYPKinjppKJkD7WQ61o%3D&h=ca9745e8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2917750001794405</a><br />\n<br />\n個官今日又唔老實。<br />\n冇真相架啦。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PrSRVyp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPrSRVyp.jpg&h=87704882&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nShawTim Liu: 0.93秒未夠時間反應<img src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/t50/1/16/1f921.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fimages%2Femoji.php%2Fv9%2Ft50%2F1%2F16%2F1f921.png&h=bed7d448&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n黃鵹: 細個成日喺屋企碌落樓梯表示：mud9<br />\n<br />\nFrancis Lee: 故意計數mess up 問題重點，spin 到佢自己爬牆墜地，咩資勢先會頭落地<img src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/t50/1/16/1f921.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fimages%2Femoji.php%2Fv9%2Ft50%2F1%2F16%2F1f921.png&h=bed7d448&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n黃鵹: 唔老實<br />\n<br />\nFrancis Lee: 主動翻牆一係屁股落地一係腰背加手肘落地，計呢堆數無意義<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nKit Wan: 陪審員計到時速36公里，猛料<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2917754088460663\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flynnleiwong%2Fposts%2F2917754088460663&d=PGKZrCzpIeFm7bz4D1EKrSlkmYPKinjppKJkD7WQ61o%3D&h=d6b60c04\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2917754088460663</a><br />\n<br />\n根據我3-16歲間豐富嘅碌落樓梯￼、sir￼扶手出軌飛落樓經驗，呢個死因庭係鬧劇。"},{"pid":"9f154d535275de04ce9c599ddb9131ab331f590b","tid":2330491,"uid":196924,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T05:20:57.000Z","msg":"0.9秒點會唔夠時間反應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54fb0d26da24cb48161bc269803568f08e382c37","tid":2330491,"uid":56219,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T05:22:21.000Z","msg":"reaction time 唔係0.2s?"},{"pid":"9a6ae94ceb076fc4dc4d6937e9398a617383a9e1","tid":2330491,"uid":53515,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T05:23:12.000Z","msg":"屌你老母小學兀櫈都撐得切隻手落地啦"},{"pid":"1de2cca8e950e1df372ee8dbdc06bcd180a0b786","tid":2330491,"uid":36481,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T05:27:23.000Z","msg":"正常都係0.5s reaction time la<br />\n成秒咁多點都會用手㩒住地下<br />\n但之前急症室醫生講過<br />\n梓樂手無擦傷<br />\n姐係有足夠反應時間下都無用手支撐<br />\n姐係昏迷左先比人掉落樓<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2aac5ac52e40048c73ff7bec09addd7912a46ff6","tid":2330491,"uid":188282,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T05:28:13.000Z","msg":"我細個10歲試過由張檯跌落地，一米多D。<br />\n個身體都識自動用膊頭果邊撞地，唔會俾個頭撞地，係本能，快到唔係自己有意識控制。"},{"pid":"5d28d042f717835f8e77c1d8f813c456e63bc902","tid":2330491,"uid":317957,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9f154d535275de04ce9c599ddb9131ab331f590b","tid":2330491,"uid":196924,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T05:20:57.000Z","msg":"0.9秒點會唔夠時間反應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T05:28:55.000Z","msg":"人仆落地下無0.93 秒都反應到 <br />\n老人家就話姐"},{"pid":"75c562738740e2ca225dfe6ed723e94edb425ef5","tid":2330491,"uid":61005,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T05:33:34.000Z","msg":"計到時速36公里有幾難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />無知真係好